# connmap performs fully static analysis over local config files.
# It NEVER connects to or authenticates against any live integration,
# so it needs no API keys, tokens, or secrets to run.
#
# This file exists only to document that fact and to satisfy tooling
# that expects a .env.example. Copy to .env if you add your own local
# tooling env vars; .env is gitignored and must never be committed.

# Optional: override the default output directory for generated reports.
# CONNMAP_OUT_DIR=./out
